Requirements for all disclosures. If Total Petroleum Initially-In-Place, Estimated Ultimate Recovery or Discovered Petroleum Initially-In-Place are disclosed by a Petroleum Reporting Entity, all of the following information must, where applicable, be prominently and proximately included in the disclosure:
(1)	an estimate of Petroleum Reserves;
